all_ingredients: Spaghetti, Eggs, Pancetta, Parmesan, Black Pepper, Olive Oil, Salt
instructions: Boil spaghetti until al dente. Fry pancetta until crispy. Whisk eggs with grated Parmesan. Toss hot spaghetti with pancetta and egg mixture off heat. Serve immediately with black pepper.

all_ingredients: Chicken, Yogurt, Tomato Paste, Cream, Onion, Garlic, Ginger, Garam Masala, Turmeric, Chili Powder, Cumin, Coriander
instructions: Marinate chicken in yogurt and spices. Grill until charred. Prepare sauce with onion, garlic, ginger, spices, tomato paste, and cream. Simmer chicken in sauce. Serve with rice or naan.

all_ingredients: Whole-grain Bread, Ripe Avocado, Lemon Juice, Salt, Pepper, Olive Oil
instructions: Toast bread slices. Mash avocado with lemon juice, salt, and pepper. Spread on toast and drizzle with olive oil.

all_ingredients: Sushi Rice, Rice Vinegar, Sugar, Salt, Nori Sheets, Fresh Fish (salmon/tuna), Avocado, Cucumber, Soy Sauce, Wasabi
instructions: Cook sushi rice, season with vinegar mixture. Lay nori, spread rice, add fillings. Roll tightly and slice. Serve with soy sauce and wasabi.

all_ingredients: Ground Beef, Taco Seasoning, Corn Tortillas, Lettuce, Tomato, Cheese, Sour Cream, Salsa
dietary_restrictions: Contains gluten, dairy (if flour tortillas/cheese used)
instructions: Brown beef with seasoning. Warm tortillas. Assemble tacos with beef, lettuce, tomato, cheese, and toppings.

all_ingredients: Tomatoes, Cucumbers, Red Onion, Kalamata Olives, Feta Cheese, Olive Oil, Oregano, Red Wine Vinegar
instructions: Chop vegetables. Mix with olives and feta. Drizzle with olive oil and vinegar, sprinkle oregano.

all_ingredients: Onions, Butter, Beef Broth, Thyme, Bay Leaf, Baguette Slices, Gruyere Cheese, Salt, Pepper
instructions: Caramelize onions in butter. Add broth and herbs, simmer 45 minutes. Ladle soup into bowls, top with bread and Gruyere, broil until melted.

all_ingredients: Chickpeas, Garlic, Onion, Parsley, Cumin, Coriander, Flour, Salt, Oil (for frying), Pita Bread, Tahini Sauce, Lettuce, Tomato
instructions: Blend chickpeas with spices and herbs. Shape into balls and fry. Serve in pita with lettuce, tomato, and tahini sauce.

all_ingredients: Bananas, Flour, Eggs, Milk, Baking Powder, Sugar, Butter, Maple Syrup
instructions: Mash bananas. Mix with flour, eggs, milk, baking powder, and sugar. Cook pancakes on skillet. Serve with butter and maple syrup.

all_ingredients: Rice Noodles, Shrimp, Egg, Tofu, Bean Sprouts, Peanuts, Tamarind Paste, Fish Sauce, Soy Sauce, Garlic, Lime
instructions: Soak rice noodles. Stir-fry shrimp, tofu, and garlic. Add noodles and sauce mixture. Push aside, scramble egg, mix together. Top with peanuts and lime.
